title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - New surprise update released
description:
In this video, we will explore the unexpected update released yesterday. This update includes the latest AIRAC cycle and, additionally, numerous airports that have been enhanced by the community through the World Hub tool. The improvements predominantly concern smaller airports, as well as those located in the US, Eastern Europe, and Asia.
